    Functional Requirements
1. Creation of classes
Enrolment - Instructor should be able to create classes and add students
2. Login Feature
Authentication - Should authenticate the different users using their email and password

3. The Dashboard 
The user interface should offer text inputs, checkboxes and sliders
Should calculate averages
The progress page should display progress for the student while markers/professors should be able to post in-text feedback and marks
Students should be able to download selected sections into report
Markers/Professors should be able to download text reports for individual students and an Excel document with studentsâ€™ marks for each class

4. Database
Storage - Should s tore student's data and their progress
Reports - Should generate individual reports for the students.
Usability - It should give support up to 120 students with private accounts that can allow them to work with up to five cases per term
Administration - Should enable admin/instructor to create dashboards, markers to grade and students to view. 


